  - "Contact administrator to reset password" message
  - "Back to Login" button
  - Full-screen centered layout matching app design

--- Step 5: Market redirect ---
Market.tsx: useEffect(() => navigate('/marketplace', { replace: true }))
/minimal rerender, no flash of content

